1931;;Out of the Blue;;British;;Gene Gerrard;;Gene Gerrard, Jessie Matthews;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Out_of_the_Blue_(1931_film);;Impoverished aristocrat's daughter Tommy Tucker (Jessie Matthews) is in love with radio announcer Bill Coverdale (Gene Gerrard), but he is engaged to her more glamorous sister Angela (Kay Hammond), who he does not love. Seeking escape from this hopeless situation, and her life of genteel poverty, Tommy flees abroad to Biarritz to become a nightclub singer.